    "The main objective of this work is to develop a model to accurately estimate the instantaneous skin-friction drag, τ ν, of surface wind waves from wave profiles, η(x), local interface slope, ∂η/∂x, local wave phases, ϕ, and the wave age of the corresponding wave field, C p /U 10.",
