    "The panels below each wave show (b, f) the local wave slope, = ∂η/∂x, (c,g) the local wave phase, ϕ, and (d,h) the skin-friction drag scaled with total stress, τ ν /τ, where the experimental data are indicated with cross symbols and the solid lines are the filtered experimental tangential stress profiles.",
